{"tid":2307922,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★父子因財困　長洲東堤小築燒炭亡","createTime":"2020-12-01T13:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T15:08:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa2ad01b984be035d41143493ad79ed9683a468","tid":2307922,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"長洲東堤小築有人燒炭。今日(12月1日)早上8時49分，警方接獲市民報案指，其中一度假屋傳出燒炭氣味，惟無人應門恐有人發生意外，遂報警求助。消防到場破門入內，發現兩名男子昏迷於單位內，經檢驗後證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後，證實死者為一對姓劉父子，分別60歲及27歲，二人分別倒臥兩張床上，旁邊有一盤燒過的炭。警方於現場檢獲遺書，案件列自殺協定，交由長洲分區刑事調查隊組跟進。至下午2時許，仵工到場將遺體舁送殮房。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，父子為裝修工人兼經營裝修工程公司，於昨日(11月30日)下午租住上址，現場留有一封遺書，內容透露因裝修公司欠債兩年，期間以信用卡貸款還債。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201201/bkn-20201201090748184-1201_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201201%2Fbkn-20201201090748184-1201_00822_001.html&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0vkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=7962c4aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201201/bkn-20201201090748184-1201_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"00be1487f15f74fec2a7e366043478afaefa805f","tid":2307922,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"all in #5 @$1XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6c32589038195a06ec1592d22fa00a4d3756aa","tid":2307922,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"上年咁多生意都做唔掂？"},{"pid":"220df8e982a6a8879424f84f20d8f0a16dc9bf06","tid":2307922,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"琴晚先睇完Ap去住長洲東堤靈探條片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca93805